title: Low Priority Queue
body:
After waiting 10 minutes it suddenly restarted. This has happened 5 times meaning i have already waited my entire penalty but have not played a single game. I have just tried to join a game and it has come up again. Im really disappointed that I cant play as i would like my first win of the day bonus :(

PLEASE HELP.

replies.body: Leavebuster is currently whack. I'm not even sure they changed it at all in the most recent patch.
